message: Hello Bob, I have a high-quality product that I'm offering for sale. Given its value and features, I'm offering it to you for $180.
Hello Alice, thanks for the offer.  $180 is a bit too high for my budget. I'd be willing to pay $70 for the product.
I appreciate your interest, Bob, but $70 is significantly below the product's value. I understand you have a budget, but I cannot go below $160 given the quality and worth of the product.
Alice, I understand the product has value, but $160 is still outside my budget.  I could go up to $85.
